id: REQ-altitude-floor
kind: requirement
name: 50 m altitude floor on goto_pixel and goto_waypoint
status: draft
description: The executor shall enforce a minimum commanded altitude of 50 m AGL on every goto_pixel and goto_waypoint command, silently raising any lower value. The floor applies only in the executor; loiter commands carry their own altitude and are not subject to this floor.
derives_from: NEED-safe-flight
verification_status: passing
satisfied_by: CMP-executor
verified_by: VER-altitude-floor
